    "id": "cp-006",
    "title": "Fix Sentry source map uploads",
    "description": "Vercel build logs show: '@sentry/nextjs - Warning: Didn't find any matching sources for debug ID upload'. Source maps not reaching Sentry, meaning stack traces in production are useless. Check sourcemaps.assets config in sentry.config.ts.",
    "status": "done",
    "priority": "medium",
    "assignee": null,
    "tags": [
      "observability",
      "sentry"
    ],
    "dependencies": [],
    "created_at": "2026-03-26T18:40:00.000Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-03-27T04:50:34.745Z",
    "assigned_agent_id": "c4304c4d-de35-45c1-9d35-e6b501464d01",
    "assigned_agent_handle": "sentinel",
    "openclaw_session_id": "capsule_pro:task-cp-006:sentinel",
    "last_agent_reply": "✅ **APPROVED**\n\n**Verification:**\n\n1. **progress.md:** Documents fix was applied - Status: complete ✓\n2. **findings.md:** Detailed root cause analysis and solution ✓\n\n**Fixes Verified:**\n- `productionBrowserSourceMaps: true` in apps/app/next.config.ts (line 161) ✓\n- `sourcemaps.assets` updated in packages/observability/next-config.ts with proper patterns ✓\n- `.sentryignore` files updated to exclude framework chunks properly ✓\n\n**Configuration Verified:**\n- Source map assets: `.next/static/chunks/app/**/*.js`, `.next/static/chunks/pages/**/*.js`, `.next/static/chunks/**/*.js`\n- `deleteSourceMapsAfterUpload: true` configured\n- Sentry release creation enabled with git commit SHA\n- Framework chunks properly excluded in .sentryignore\n\nThe fix addresses the root cause: production source maps were disabled, and sourcemaps.assets patterns were too restrictive. The changes are correct and complete. Ready for deployment verification.",
    "reviewed_at": "2026-03-27T04:50:34.745Z"
  },
